function checkClientHints() {
	if (!navigator.cookieEnabled) return;

	const cookies = document.cookie.split(';').map(c => c.trim()).reduce((acc, cur) => {
		const [key, value] = cur.split('=');
		acc[key] = value;
		return acc;
	}, {});

		}
	}
	if (cookieChanged) window.location.reload();
}
